{"tid":1259993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"現在搵狗大法 快而準！","createTime":"2019-06-26T17:30:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T18:06:45.000Z","uid":255970,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"340b5422baacfabdd25dc0467b82e973b6d8f3c6","tid":1259993,"uid":255970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0emYnL9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0emYnL9.png&h=482d93fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警總示威 之 問米</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n一直以嚟警察陰濕蠱惑，成鳩日混入人群搞事，今晚又差啲畀佢陰鳩左，希望喺每次衝突嘅現場，搵出邊啲係差佬。（雖然差佬有時好易認）<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得要「問米」，搵啲鬼出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n例如，今晚喺聚集咗群眾之後，發起「問米行動」，讓群眾<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">禮貌地、唔傷和氣地</span></span>，詢問前後左右四個人：「你係唔係警務人員？」<br />\n<br />\n根據過往嘅經驗，似乎喺現場嘅差佬，無論幾撚口面皮都好，佢哋都唔敢否認而講自己唔係差佬。搵完出嚟就name and shame。<br />\n<br />\n（當然一旦發現左，就要影住佢。呢啲都係經常性唔使講。）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KtC8KZx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKtC8KZx.png&h=7728140b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38f460e7efcf13a82fda8f5469c28c5d647f4b9e","tid":1259993,"uid":140802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"幾黑都好 比人影住問 佢一定唔可以答唔係<br />\n如果唔係比人發現佢講大話佢就仆硬街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86b17db4fa12afae09fe04361286b8f5a7644b3","tid":1259993,"uid":164190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:47:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"325d65f9df677bb8ef92d91bbabd0090ca91a6ff","tid":1259993,"uid":164190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d2cbcc24944c9e32a5e03fd5f6a2bb0